trans-unit.source: Supplies base class implementation for all activity designer theme classes used in a workflow design-time environment.
trans-unit.target: Utstyr basere Klasseimplementering for alle aktiviteten designer tema klasser som brukes i et miljø for utforming av arbeidsflyten.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] All classes that supply theme property settings to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> classes must inherit from the DesignerTheme class.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Alle klasser som oppgi tema egenskapsinnstillingene <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner>klasser må</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> arve fra DesignerTheme klasse.

trans-unit.source: Designer themes provide a set of property values with which to display background and foreground colors and styles, fonts, and other style settings for the designer classes displayed on a workflow design surface.
trans-unit.target: Spørringsutformer oppsett inneholder et sett med verdier som skal vises bakgrunnen og forgrunnen farger og stiler, skrifter og andre Stilinnstillinger for designer klassene vises på en arbeidsflyt utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientTheme> class also inherits from DesignerTheme.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientTheme>klassen arver også fra DesignerTheme.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientTheme>

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"></xref> class by using a <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Når implementert i en avledet klasse, initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av en <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme"></xref> with which the designer theme is associated.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme"> </xref> med som designer tema er knyttet til.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the unqualified name of the designer type to which the designer theme is applied.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på ukvalifiserte av typen designer designer tema brukes.

trans-unit.source: The ApplyTo property associates the designer theme with a designer by using the unqualified name of the designer type, while the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.DesignerType%2A> property associates the designer theme with a designer type by using the <xref:System.Type> of the designer.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ApplyTo knytter designer tema designer ved å bruke ukvalifiserte navn av typen designer mens den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.DesignerType%2A>egenskapen knytter designer tema typen designer ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Type>av designer.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.DesignerType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the designer type to which the designer theme is applied.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på designer typen designer tema brukes.

trans-unit.source: A user attempted a set operation when the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.ReadOnly*> property was set to <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En bruker forsøkte en set-operasjon når den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.ReadOnly*>-egenskap er satt til <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.ReadOnly*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the workflow theme that encapsulates the designer theme.
trans-unit.target: Henter arbeidsflyten tema som innkapsler designer tema.

trans-unit.source: The ContainingTheme property returns the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme> object that the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.%23ctor%2A> used during initialization.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer ContainingTheme den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme>objekt som den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.%23ctor%2A>brukes under initialisering.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.%23ctor%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme"></xref> object associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme"> </xref> tilknyttet den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of the designer associated with the designer theme.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir typen utformingen tilknyttet designer tema.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerType property associates the designer theme with a designer type by using the <xref:System.Type> of the designer, while the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.ApplyTo%2A> property associates the designer theme with a designer by using the unqualified name of the designer type.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen DesignerType knytter designer tema typen designer ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Type>av designer, mens den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.ApplyTo%2A>egenskapen knytter designer tema designer ved å bruke ukvalifiserte navn av typen designer.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.ApplyTo%2A> </xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Possible values for this property include <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner>, and any classes created by activity designer developers that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme>.
trans-unit.target: Mulige verdier for denne egenskapen inkluderer <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner>, og alle klasser som er opprettet av aktiviteten designer utviklere som arver fra <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Type> that represents the designer to be associated with the current designer theme.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Type>som representerer designer som skal knyttes til gjeldende designer tema.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A user attempted a set operation when the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.ReadOnly*> property was set to <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En bruker forsøkte en set-operasjon når den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.ReadOnly*>-egenskap er satt til <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.ReadOnly*>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"> </xref> og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Allows the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"></xref> to attempt to free resources and perform other clean-up operations before it is reclaimed by garbage collection.
trans-unit.target: Gjør den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"> </xref> under forsøk på å frigjøre ressurser og utføre andre operasjoner for opprydding før den er gode av datasanering.

trans-unit.source: Finalize releases only unmanaged resources prior to garbage collection.
trans-unit.target: Fullfør versjoner bare uforvaltede ressurser før datasanering.

trans-unit.source: Performs further initialization tasks beyond those performed by <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.%23ctor%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Utfører ytterligere initialisering oppgaver utover de som utføres av <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme.%23ctor%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme> class provides no default behavior for this method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme>klassen gir ingen standard virkemåte for denne metoden.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme>

trans-unit.source: Classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme> must provide their own logic for this method.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som arver fra <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme>må angi sitt eget logikken for denne metoden.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme>

trans-unit.source: Notifies the designer theme class that the ambient property settings for the designer have changed.
trans-unit.target: Varsler designer tema klassen som de omsluttende egenskapsinnstillingene for designer er endret.

trans-unit.source: Classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme> use this method to make necessary changes when the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> enumeration value changes from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som arver fra <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme>Bruk denne metoden for å gjøre nødvendig endrer når <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>opplisting verdiendringer fra <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>eller <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>til <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> enumeration determines where a designer theme obtains its ambient property settings.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>opplisting bestemmer hvor et designer tema anskaffer egenskapsinnstillingene omkringliggende.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> value is set, the designer theme class obtains its ambient settings from the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.AmbientTheme%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>verdi angis, klassen designer tema anskaffer omkringliggende innstillingene fra den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.AmbientTheme%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.AmbientTheme%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty> value is set, the designer theme class obtains its ambient settings from the operating system on which the designer is installed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>verdi angis, klassen designer tema henter omkringliggende innstillingene fra operativsystemet som designer er installert.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty"></xref> enumeration value that the designer theme should now use.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.AmbientProperty"> </xref> opplistingsverdien designer tema nå skal bruke.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the designer theme is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer tema er skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme> that the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme> is initialized with is not a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), ReadOnly obtains its value from the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.ReadOnly%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme>som den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme>er initialisert er ikke et nullreferanse (`Nothing` i Visual Basic), ReadOnly henter verdien fra det <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.ReadOnly%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.ReadOnly%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme> is a null reference (`Nothing`), ReadOnly is `false`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme>er en nullreferanse (`Nothing`), er skrivebeskyttet `false`.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme> is assigned to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.CurrentTheme%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, the ReadOnly property is set to `true`, and properties on all designer themes associated with this theme cannot be changed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme>er tilordnet til den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.CurrentTheme%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, ReadOnly-egenskapen er satt til `true`, og egenskapene i alle designer oppsett som er tilknyttet denne tema kan ikke endres.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.CurrentTheme%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme>

trans-unit.source: If required, properties can be set after loading the theme but before assigning it to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.CurrentTheme%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Om nødvendig kan egenskaper angis etter innlasting av oppsettet, men før du tilordner til <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.CurrentTheme%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.WorkflowTheme.CurrentTheme%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"></xref> is read-only; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerTheme"> </xref> er skrivebeskyttet; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Performs application-defined tasks associated with freeing, releasing, or resetting unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: Utfører Programdefinert oppgaver som er forbundet med frigjøring, frigi eller tilbakestille uforvaltede ressurser.
